reviewText: I watch tons of paranormal shows & movies, as they are very intriguing to me.  In my opinion, series like A Haunting, My Haunted House & Paranormal Witness are really well made shows and actually kinda scary.  Both Conjuring movies and all the Paranormal Activity movies were horrifying to me, which is why we watch.  These Most Haunted shows, in my opinion, SUCK!  They are in comparison to the series Ghostly Encounters.  Not scary, nor very interesting.
Good program. Not great, but good!
Not too bad but I have seen better.
